WEBVTT

00:00.899 --> 00:02.336
<i>Previously on "Quantico"...</i>

00:02.339 --> 00:04.304
ENGIN is an avionic startup.

00:04.307 --> 00:05.766
The government just
signed a billion-dollar

00:05.768 --> 00:07.207
contract with them this morning.

00:07.210 --> 00:08.550
I have feelings for you.

00:08.585 --> 00:10.052
Where are you going?

00:10.086 --> 00:11.492
Goodbye, Shelby.

00:11.495 --> 00:13.122
You ruined the operation.

00:13.156 --> 00:14.549
And you ruined my only chance

00:14.552 --> 00:16.821
to get my sister out of who knows where.

00:16.824 --> 00:17.724
How many people die

00:17.727 --> 00:19.461
if the Collaborators
reach their endgame?

00:19.496 --> 00:21.997
- We don't know what their endgame is!
- Exactly.

00:22.032 --> 00:24.733
Now I will, because I'm on the inside.

00:24.768 --> 00:26.335
We transition tomorrow.

00:26.369 --> 00:27.937
Welcome to the team.

00:27.971 --> 00:31.674
I'm not resigning because I
believe I did anything wrong.

00:31.708 --> 00:34.234
As no vice president
has yet been confirmed,

00:34.237 --> 00:36.976
Speaker of the House Henry Roarke

00:36.979 --> 00:39.014
will take the oath of that office.

00:39.049 --> 00:40.282
It's only a matter of time

00:40.317 --> 00:41.750
before someone sends the FBI

00:41.785 --> 00:44.053
to arrest her and us for treason.

00:45.989 --> 00:48.991
♪

